Dashboard Heroes Search
=======================

Tags: dashboard,search

As manager of a heroes agency

* I load the "Dashboard" page
* Then I see the "Top Heroes" header

Scenario 1: Search Matching no Heroes
-------------------------------------

* I type "Superman" on the search field
* Then I see no heroes on the search's result

Scenario 2: Search Matching one Hero
-----------------------------------

* I type "Narco" on the search field
* The search's result contains "Narco"

scenario 3: Search Matching Multiple Heroes
-------------------------------------------

* I type "Na" on the search field
* Then I see "3" heroes on the search's result
* The search's result contains "Narco"
* The search's result contains "Dynama"
* The search's result contains "Tornado"

